reviewText: Little slow for my kids. I had five kids doing this workout and only the youngest ages six and eight were even slightly interested.
My sic year old son and I love this!
My second graders love this, and I tried it out myself yesterday and really liked it as well.  A few of my students said it made them feel relaxed.
I watched the whole video and also had my 6-7 year olds try it.. they found it boring & too difficutl..
